Class FuncHeader

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.tymeac.base.FuncHeader

  • public final class FuncHeader
extends java.lang.Object
    Tymeac Function header contains the Function array setup, the search methods for finding an entry and the methods for accessing the detail array.

      • addFunction

        protected void addFunction(java.lang.String name,
               AreaBase agent,
               AreaBase[] Q)
        New function, call the detail add method. When at end, check for dup hash codes. When any dups, we cannot use a hash code search, therefore, we need to sort the String function names.
        Parameters:
        name - String - function name
        agent - AreaBase - output agent queue number
        Q - AreaBase[] - queue array
